		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Sweet exp and loot for lvl's 12-17<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Sweet exp and loot for lvl's 12-17";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Thu, Aug 24th 8:39 PM2000 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=8&mid=96716397825790&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=8&mid=96716397825790&num=2&page=0&post=1&replyto=96716397825790"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=96716397825790></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=455"><span id=>Igota</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br />7 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [4.25]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Igota&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Err, make that lvl's 13-17. hehe.<br>Zone is Southern Desert of Ro.<br><br>In the South West corner of the desert there is a Bandit camp. It is a three spawn with a fourth out in front (at the tip of the gully). We are, once again, the best class for this camp because we have Harmony, which allows us to solo it (and we all know that soloing is waayyy better exp and loot). <br><br>At lvl 12 this is pretty hard and you might have to call on someone&#8217;s help to rip the higher lvl ones for you (do NOT ask a lvl 40+ to help you kill it, it is much easier for them to just kill it and be on their way then protect your hide). One great thing about this zone is that there are ALWAYS a few 45+&#8217;s camping the AC, and most have no objections to buffing you (but as always make your request a full sentence and be polite/funny, it will get you much more then just saying &#8220;buffs plz&#8221;). A clarity here and there will make your exp roll in about twice fast. And the more friends you make here, because you were nice, they will most likely remember you later and will stand up for you when you need it. <br><br>The best way to kill these Bandits is to start on the south side of the camp and pull between the zone wall and the pillar, harmony the camp (takes one casting) and pull the one who is alone with a Snare, burn a few times while running away, cast a dmg shield on yourself, turn and beat on them for a bit until they are dead, med to full, harmony the camp and pull the one that is closest to you. You should be able to find a good balance of how much mana to use per fight, if both your HP and MP get to full at the same time while you are medding then you have it down. <br><br>Once you get your new rank of spells at 14 (if you have a good conjuration) use Stinging Swarm after you pull with Snare.<br><br>These Bandits, as is standard, have pretty good loot, (dropping as much as 7 gold and the not too rare bronze weapon). The good loot, short down time (thank you Enchanters), and fat exp from soloing effectively will make you rich and lvl 17 before you can blink.<br></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />--<br>Dinivan Silvermane, Druid of Erolissi Marr.<br>Igota Reallife, Warlord in training, Erolissi Marr.</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >2 Replies</td></tr></table>
